Texas Chukwu, Abuja: Troops deployed in Exercise AYEM AKPATUMA in Taraba State in conjunction with personnel of the Nigeria Police on 31 March 2018 arrested some criminal elements operating in Mayo Ndaga of Taraba State. Items recovered from one of the suspects Amos Titus- 35, include sheets of zinc, bed and locally made pistol. Other suspects Palat Jafainal- 20 and Kingsley Benson- 25 were also arrested and items recovered from them include generating set, sewing machine as well as sheets of zinc. One Rapheal Abel- 26 and Yusuf Abdulkareem- 20 from Kaka Tribe were also arrested and sheets of zinc were recovered from them. A.M Tanimu is an Online Editor with Africa's Largest TV Network. With a decade experience in Television journalism, and a graduate of University of Maiduguri. Tanimu also produces TV shows with NTA when not on Social media.